{"tid":317941,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人近排係咁亂洗錢？","createTime":"2017-07-11T19:25:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-11T23:57:50.000Z","uid":118884,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f455b3cf48a7d68266dae9a5fd131c28be204ba1","tid":317941,"uid":118884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T19:25:59.000Z","msg":"上年畢完業到黎家差唔多半年多d<br />\n儲左幾皮野就開始黎料<br />\n成日心郁郁想買野<br />\n近排又買iPad pro switch<br />\n今日又忍唔到手買gundam黎玩<br />\n下個月仲訂左splatoon2<br />\n仲未計平時買埋d小遊戲<br />\n雞毛蒜皮既錢<br />\n我知道根本玩唔哂<br />\n雖然唔係洗到1$都無<br />\n但根本每個月都儲唔到錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔知係番工壓力太大定點<br />\n一見到有少少想買既野就好想買<br />\n成日覺得番工咁辛苦<br />\n仲要就住就住用就搞到黎家咁<br />\n由食飯唔睇價錢到黎家咩都買一餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成日個心同自己講要儲錢<br />\n但又唔想抑壓自己買野既情緒<br />\n求巴絲打比下意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n斬手指剪卡都要忍住儲錢既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今日開心理撚得佢既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8558ca76e66447a72a9bb1cfe5c88de2319099d8","tid":317941,"uid":118884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T19:27:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02f77017e0f069cc0ee993a29c5ad46ada2f0571","tid":317941,"uid":89146,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T19:28:38.000Z","msg":"儲錢嘅意義為左咩?<br />\n買樓? 你買到咩<br />\n買唔到又儲黎做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n及時行樂啦"},{"pid":"0ce1ae8f0d98871f7e281c626d5fb72ec5aac04a","tid":317941,"uid":33004,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T19:32:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>儲錢嘅意義為左咩?<br />\n買樓? 你買到咩<br />\n買唔到又儲黎做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n及時行樂啦</blockquote><br />\n有咁既思想真係好撚廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5bc68df39751d06d6ac88fdfc0484193d9bde4d","tid":317941,"uid":118884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T19:36:21.000Z","msg":"上面個兩個留言搞到我仲矛盾<br />\n聽邊個好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e7dee19fafc652aa778ee1a480488ad6d0da013","tid":317941,"uid":62345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T19:39:55.000Z","msg":"積穀防饑"},{"pid":"8d7a9121658166eb20e9c9f8a51185e802e7e16e","tid":317941,"uid":40550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T19:40:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上面個兩個留言搞到我仲矛盾<br />\n聽邊個好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n聽乜春呀人地既做法又未必適合你<br />\n<br />\n點解有人死慳爛慳都要買樓？<br />\n因為樓對佢地黎講好重要，可以為佢地帶來前所未有既滿足<br />\n咁你問下自己，樓對你黎講重唔重要呢？<br />\nShopping 重要啲？食好野重要啲？旅行重要啲？"},{"pid":"169da1ba4e5676c382fbd129eac72c35466f5cd4","tid":317941,"uid":86943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T19:42:20.000Z","msg":"及時行樂最重要，有啲嘢你唔做會後悔一世"},{"pid":"df64f448d5fe29701f20f90d07533004cc80a779","tid":317941,"uid":86943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T19:43:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>及時行樂最重要，有啲嘢你唔做會後悔一世</blockquote><br />\n(錢嘅話儲二十萬左右，應急就算)"},{"pid":"a3fff3c7ef01fdb22dd75f6f0fe9502a76c42842","tid":317941,"uid":32981,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T23:43:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>儲錢嘅意義為左咩?<br />\n買樓? 你買到咩<br />\n買唔到又儲黎做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n及時行樂啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n儲錢一定係為買樓架咩？<br />\n儲黎買架車，請老豆老母去旅行，老左黎醫病都得掛"},{"pid":"3a0c00c591aaf5cc465ac227ff2abccba305a121","tid":317941,"uid":123605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T23:57:50.000Z","msg":"少少積蓄點都要有<br />\n剩低就自己諗吓應該點用<br />\n但唔好用哂錢然後呻窮<br />\n然後賴個社會呢樣嗰樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}